aym fiylaxng mahch behter naw towd sehd fraag ay downt thihngk ay niyd ax staoriy ehniymaor

rayt

dhaets dhax pihg faemaxliy axn ax paxliys kaar
drayvaxng ax paxliys kaar
hhuwz axn baek ahv dhehm dhaets ax guhd kwehschaxn

aend dhehn waht hhaepaxnz

ihts rehd
